{"tid":2233443,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"阮民安探訪68歲張叔叔「的士司機手足」","createTime":"2020-10-07T06:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T00:29:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":113,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"882188c53294f8c4f0700dbba1b9079b12da2986","tid":2233443,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120838572_3503603416366934_1201096555689835922_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=0-lklTKP-L0AX-C4WxN&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=3bfc0a00967501a38206cb927796e659&amp;oe=5FA12967\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120838572_3503603416366934_1201096555689835922_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3D0-lklTKP-L0AX-C4WxN%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D3bfc0a00967501a38206cb927796e659%26oe%3D5FA12967&h=19534a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120818807_3503603499700259_7004748783006871089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=RNFL79N7D_MAX9wySfa&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=49611d187c6fb9990e095effa1baa44b&amp;oe=5FA3CF4B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120818807_3503603499700259_7004748783006871089_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DRNFL79N7D_MAX9wySfa%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D49611d187c6fb9990e095effa1baa44b%26oe%3D5FA3CF4B&h=904b11f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120852672_3503603586366917_6218456504118162897_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=lhNBud_G1nsAX_0IcjA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=3d2ac8fc7729f46b0b2bc8173fcf9091&amp;oe=5FA1070C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120852672_3503603586366917_6218456504118162897_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DlhNBud_G1nsAX_0IcjA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D3d2ac8fc7729f46b0b2bc8173fcf9091%26oe%3D5FA1070C&h=f7209c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阮民安 - Tommy<br />\n<br />\n今日凍左好多，一早就去左荔枝角探個老手足！<br />\n手足們，還記得喺上年7月7日晚，喺旺角用自己架車擋住d黑警同狗車，保護前線手足，我地稱佢為香港的逆權司機個老手足嗎？<br />\n呢一擋，起碼救左十幾二十個手足！<br />\n今年佢已經68歲了。<br />\n原來佢一路好想同我食到一餐飯，但因為怕唔好意思，所以無邀約。<br />\n上個月答辯完，就開始還押左喺荔枝角了。<br />\n今個月12號正式判刑，佢個女話希望喺佢爸爸正式判刑之前，可以還佢心願見一見我，同我傾下偈。<br />\n老手足，我嚟左啦！<br />\n嗰晚您嘅勇敢，我自愧不如。我哋好多手足都擔心您有事啊～<br />\n佢同我講：<br />\n無事，呢度有四十幾個手足，互相照應，無問題呀！一生人可以為大家做到件咁啱嘅事，我好高興呀~<br />\n唔知最後判刑結果如何，但我再次替所有手足祝您好人有好報，一生平安！<br />\n手足們，就算無左街頭抗爭，都仲有好多野可以做的啊～<br />\n加油！盡做吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/802472909813345/posts/3503603639700245/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F802472909813345%2Fposts%2F3503603639700245%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=ee11097f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/802472909813345/posts/3503603639700245/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b98c891abfe1ea6b9e99dc13ec5c19e445306b5f","tid":2233443,"uid":76804,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"之前一路怪錯佢<br />\n原來佢先係最有心果個黎<br />\n之前派口罩要藍絲講黑警死全家<br />\n成日探手足<br />\n<br />\n近幾次都有出黎遊行<br />\n好早開始已經有出黎<br />\n仲要比人話佢搏出位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250be811f64550a4e7194dfd2eddb4c403e1cc02","tid":2233443,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528a342854d379a6bc228079115cf10b2dc96721","tid":2233443,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b98c891abfe1ea6b9e99dc13ec5c19e445306b5f","tid":2233443,"ui